# NanoClaw Environment File
# Copy to ~/.nanoclaw/env and fill in values
# This file is sourced by launchd plists and container entrypoints

# === Claude Authentication (required â€” pick one) ===
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oau01-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# === Home Assistant (required for ha-mcp sidecar) ===
# HA_URL=http://homeassistant.local:8123
# HA_TOKEN=<long-lived-access-token>
# Generate at: Home Assistant > Profile > Long-Lived Access Tokens
# Note: ha-mcp-web expects HOMEASSISTANT_URL/HOMEASSISTANT_TOKEN env vars.
# The setup script maps HA_URL -> HOMEASSISTANT_URL and HA_TOKEN -> HOMEASSISTANT_TOKEN
# when installing the launchd plist.

# === NanoClaw HTTP API (required for voice plugin / external integrations) ===
# NANOCLAW_API_TOKEN=<generate-a-random-secret>
